result.name: 好日子皇宴

reviews.text: Average dim sum with steady quality. Not too difficult to find seats. As a neighbourhood restaurant, not a bad choice.
Some of the dishes are not making sense. Weird handling of ingredients.(eg tomato in deep fried salad roll.)

Better than i expected while paying my respects in the area. The Tea & Food was piping hot which was a refreshing comparing to more expensive and tarted up restaurants in many other areas from TKO, HK Island to Tung Chung.
Value for money and pretty good food and showed at least on the occasion i went there that they had got the fundamentals right. It reflects the traditional dimsum places that are still around.
If you are a nit picker then the decor may not be 5 star or attentive as some newer eateries. This is a local traditional Chinese restaurant and comes with it the traditiinal atmosphere and experience such as being proactive to ger attention, ordering and cutlery has the distinct whiff of bleach that many older eateries have. Germs or Bleach, well as the lesser of the two evils bleach at least its clean. Its traditional and many locals will rinse the utensils before using anyway.
Cheap and delicious, but services is not good
So far so good

result.name: 好日子皇宴

reviews.text: 好日子皇宴酒樓，是一間中型酒樓，菜色及味道也很好，有很多茶客，生意不錯。
梅菜扣肉可吃一半 蒸魚火喉尚欠 奇怪地上座率不俗 個人冇下次
地方都算大，點心OK，有泊車，平時1O點入閘，消費200百可享二小時免費泊車，星期六，日，消費300 百元可亨二小時免費泊車。
全日早，午，晚收費貴左小小，枱椅有的壁窄，明星相比好好多，食物，價錢合理
早茶時間 中間檯位大密 進食小心被人撞上
